snippet.title: OpenXcom 1.0 Feature Trailer
snippet.description:
OpenXcom is an open-source clone of the original X-Com. Download it now at https://openxcom.org

Trailer music used:
- "Evil Plan" by Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com) 
Licensed under Creative Commons: By Attribution 3.0
http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/
- Original Intro music by John Broomhall
- "Geoscape Part II" by Lorcán: http://www.lorcan.be/

Mods featured in this video downloaded from https://openxcom.mod.io/

Follow us on:
https://www.facebook.com/openxcom
https://www.twitter.com/openxcom

Thanks to everyone that helped make this happen!
